Package: ctesiphus
Title: Ctesiphus Expedition Campaign Manager
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("League", "Facilitator", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Kill Team Summer League campaign manager for the Ctesiphus
    Expedition rules (Dead Silence pack): a pure-functional R rules engine
    (dice, hex geometry, exploration, and the movement/battle/action/threat
    phases), a PostgreSQL persistence bridge, and a mobile-first Shiny app.
